-- AIG to Raise About $6 Billion From Sale of Shares in Asian Insurer AIA
-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 2012-03-06T00:17:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-06/aig-to-raise-6-billion-selling-aia-shares-at-hk-27-15-each-in-hong-kong.html
American International Group Inc. (AIG) 
will sell 1.72 billion shares of  AIA Group Ltd. (1299)  to institutional
investors for HK$27.15 (about $3.50) each for gross proceeds of
about $6 billion.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
